---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
import Picture from '../../components/core/Picture.astro';
---
<section>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="py-12 md:py-20">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-[3.50rem] font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading">Hola! Me llamo Josa Vicente</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center pb-10 md:pb-16">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-[3.50rem] font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading">
                    <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-secondary-500">Engineer Manager</span> +
                    <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-primary-500 sm:whitespace-nowrap"
                        >Developer</span
                    >
                </h1>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="relative mb-8 m-auto max-w-3xl mt-8">
                    <Picture
                        src={import('../../assets/images/hero.png')}
                        class="mx-auto rounded-md bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 w-full"
                        widths={[400, 768]}
                        sizes=" (max-width: 767px) 400px, 768px"
                        alt="Hero Image"
                        aspectRatio="16:9"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 dark:text-slate-400 text-b">
                Llevo desde los 14 años programando, empecé con turbo Pascal a hacer mis primeros programas. Ahora, con 42 años
                considero que saber programar el stack de moda no es suficiente. Unas buenas bases, conocimientos de arquitectura y testing
                así como unas soft skills fuertes para trabajar en equipo son esenciales. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-none px-6 flex flex-nowrap flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-center gap-4">
            <div class="flex w-full sm:w-auto">
                <a
                    class="btn text-white border border-primary-600 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-800 hover:border-primary-800 sm:mb-0 w-full"
                    href="https://github.com/onwidget/astrowind"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener"
                >
                <Icon name="tabler:brand-hipchat" class="w-5 h-5 mr-1 -ml-1.5" /> 
                    Get template
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex w-full sm:w-auto">
                <a class="btn text-white bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 w-full" href="#features">Learn more</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>        
    </div>
</section>
